name: Diabetes Dataset
data_intro: This dataset is originally from the National Institute of Diabetes and Digestive and Kidney Diseases. The objective is to predict based on diagnostic measurements whether a patient has diabetes.

num_feature_intro.Glucose: 2. Plasma glucose concentration a 2 hours in an oral glucose tolerance test
num_feature_intro.BMI: - BMI: Body mass index (weight in kg/(height in m)^2)
